adidas Pure Slip-On Human Made Black
description: The Human Made x Pure Slip-On 'Black' released as part of a three-shoe collection with Nigo's workwear-inspired label. Modeled after an archival kung fu shoe the laceless upper is built with mesh supported by a stretchy textile heel and finished in Core Black. Human Made branding emerges on the vamp while underfoot a wedge Boost midsole in contrasting white provides cushioning giving way to a cored-out gum rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: adidas Pure Slip-On Human Made Cream White
description: Made in collaboration with Nigo's label the Human Made x Pure Slip-On 'Cream White' is itself inspired by a vintage kung fu shoe discovered by Nigo in adidas' archives. Built with mesh the shoe's slip-on construction sports a Cream White finish with a textile inner lining supporting the fit. The vamp adds a tonal Human Made logo while underfoot full-length Boost provides cushioning giving way to a cored-out gum rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: Nike Air Streak Lite Back On Track
adidas Pure Slip-On Human Made Wild Pine
description: The Human Made x Pure Slip-On 'Wild Pine' features inspiration from an archival kung fu shoe. Made in collaboration with Nigo's workwear-inspired label the shoe's upper appears in Wild Pine on its ventilated mesh construction with the vamp sporting oversized Human Made branding. Underfoot a white full-length Boost midsole provides cushioning and contrast giving way to a gum rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: adidas Dame 3 On Tour
Nike Wildhorse 6 Off Noir
description: The Zoom Wildhorse 6 'Black' brings a neutral look to its trail construction. The shoe's upper is built with ripstop and mesh supported by a no-sew overlay on the toe. A heel pull-loop provides easy on and off while a white Swoosh contrasts the side wall. Underfoot a two-tone phylon midsole provides cushioning giving way to a lugged rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: Nike Air Skylon 2 Fear of God White
description: In this collaboration with his Fear of God brand Jerry Lorenzo is updating the classic Air Skylon 2. Tonal leather and suede overlays complement a white textile foundation with a patent leather Swoosh in comparison to black. There is an unbranded perforated leather tongue in matching white underneath the toggle lacing scheme.

shoeName: Nike Air Skylon 2 Fear of God Black Sail
description: Nike collaborated with Fear of God’s Jerry Lorenzo to launch an upgraded version of the Skylon 2 silhouette. The Fear Of God x Air Skylon 2 'Black' features a mesh-based upper dipped in all black with coordinated leather and patent leather details. The low top also is equipped with mesh padding on the tongue for ventilation a toggle lacing system for a secure fit and Fear of God logo on the heel side and insole.
